Conclusion:
Because Candidate 1 couples cinematic, expansive arrangements and meticulous mastering with multi‑part harmonies, inventive two‑disc sequencing and clearly documented physical credits — all features that directly reflect my stated tastes for layered, melodic, well‑mastered, start‑to‑finish listening experiences — it is the better match. Candidate 2 is compelling as concept prog, but it lacks the specific production and packaging signals (multi‑part vocal arrangements, pop/prog melodic balance, clear pressing/mastering documentation and multi‑disc sequencing) that tip the choice in favor of the Ambitious pop/prog double‑album.

