The positive CD has the following updated information: Keyboard‑forward hits compilation with upfront, close vocals that frequently overshadow drums and bass. Bright synth/piano pushes midrange, heavier limiting reduces headroom and transient snap; thin low end, compressed feel, brief booklet/notes — appeals to those prioritizing vocals and hits over rhythmic depth or collector transfers.

